snippet.title: Tripping balls: Woman high on drugs takes a walk through NYC

localized.description:
Viral video of woman high on drugs in NYC: Video shot in New York on Sunday of a woman in distress (and clothes several sizes too small) is going viral online.  In the video the woman, apparently named Angie, appears to be under the influence of a powerful narcotic. Medical responders gingerly attempt to restrain her before eventually loading her into an ambulance. 

The six-minute long video was uploaded to Liveleak on October 14 and has been viewed more than 400,000 times in just 48 hours. Little else is known about the unsettling footage.
